  "description": "Resolve all defects found in the Deep Audit v2 for `hx-accordion`.\nSource: `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-accordion/AUDIT.md`\n\n**Summary:** 13 defects — 2 P0, 4 P1, 2 P2, 5 P3\n\n### P0 — Critical\n- [ ] [CRITICAL] 1: `_handleToggle` calls `preventDefault()` on non-cancellable `toggle` event\n- [ ] [CRITICAL] 2: Single-mode sibling collapse does not dispatch `hx-collapse` events\n\n### P1 — High\n- [ ] [HIGH] 1: Arrow key navigation not implemented (WCAG 2.1 SC 2.1.1)\n- [ ] [HIGH] 2: Double opacity on disabled items (WCAG 2.1 SC 1.4.3)\n- [ ] [HIGH] 3: Disabled items remain keyboard-focusable\n- [ ] [HIGH] 4: Multiple expanded items in single mode not resolved on connect\n\n### P2 — Medium\n- [ ] [MEDIUM] 1: Inline SVG chevron recreated on every render\n- [ ] [MEDIUM] 2: CSS `:not()` selector with descendant combinator (Level 4)\n\n### P3 — Low\n- [ ] [Unknown] `itemId` defaults to empty string\n- [ ] [Unknown] CSS part naming differs from common patterns\n- [ ] [Unknown] No story with icon-in-header pattern\n- [ ] [Unknown] No axe-core automated a11y tests\n- [ ] [Unknown] `aria-expanded` explicit on `<summary>`\n\nReference the AUDIT.md in the component directory for full details and code locations.",
